::Aerotaur::
       He sends a reply.  "I think the better question is who isn't attacking 
us.  Most of our former enemies and a few new ones are out there pounding our 
shields.  Fortunately we're well defended but we could use some backup.  
Thanks for coming to help us."  He shuts down the link and turns to the 
others. "The Maximals are on their way.  They'll help us.  Then we can hide 
ourselves in a new location.
